headline: SKIPPY® Crushin' It Tour Celebrates Student Hustle with Peanut Butter on College Campuses
summary: The SKIPPY® brand is hitting the road with the SKIPPY® Crushin' It tour; an initiative designed to celebrate and support students and student-athletes as they head back to school. The tour includes high-energy campus events; a peanut butter giveaway and product donations aimed at addressing food insecurity — a persistent problem on college campuses nationwide.
